    " #### Q4: What is the most purchased item on the menu and how many times was it purchased by all customers?\n",
    " "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      " * sqlite://\n",
      "Done.\n"
